claim.claim-text:
An information processing device comprising:
a position input unit configured to receive a position input;
an input-frequency measurement unit configured to measure the frequency of inputs where the position input unit has received the position input;
a distance calculation unit configured to calculate a distance between a reference position obtained owing to the position input and a current input position;
a drag determining unit configured to determine whether or not being a drag input, on the basis of a movement amount of an input position obtained from the position input unit;
a mode controller configured to cause a display mode in a display unit to transition to a certain mode on the basis of a judgment result in the drag determining unit and the frequency of inputs in the input-frequency measurement unit; and
a display content setting unit configured to perform a setting so as to change a display content on a screen to a certain zoom factor corresponding to a distance, on the basis of the distance obtained from the distance calculation unit and a movement direction obtained from the drag determining unit, when a transition to a zoom mode has occurred owing to the mode controller.
